/ur5e/controller_manager/introspection_data/values
/ur5e/controller_manager/statistics/full
/ur5e/controller_manager/statistics/names
/ur5e/controller_manager/statistics/values
/ur5e/joint_states
/ur5e/robot_description
Is it okay, that /tf and /tf_static is not namespaced?
  
  
   -->